      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KRAKEN WHISKY (4) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with three wins and a placing from six tries. Missed the frame latest (21.92) when fourth over 390m at this track in a Special conditions H. Has the ability and should feature. RIGHTEOUS FURY (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by a long neck at Warragul in a handy 22.67 beating Paw Kristelle. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Sure to measure up. PIEBALD (1) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 2 lengths (24.68) behind Playback at Traralgon. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Can measure up. FAYE VALENTINE (7) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
